The airplane you are on is unique.
While many airlines have Boeing 707's,
this one has been totally refurbished and has
many completely new features to give you
the most pleasurable ride in the air.
This aircraft was specially designed for
the long-distance domestic routes of TWA's
exclusive Ambassador Service. But we also
fly it on shorter routes, many times a day,
which means you can often enjoy it even if
you're not on an Ambassador Service flight.
Note: The back cover of this piece is also a "Seat Occupied" card.
Please feel free to use it if you have to leave your seat.
